---
import '../styles/global.css';
---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Static Nav Debug</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
  </head>
  <body class="bg-gray-900 text-white">
    <nav id="static-test-nav" class="fixed top-0 inset-x-0 z-50 bg-gray-900/90 backdrop-blur border-b border-gray-800">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto h-16 px-4 flex items-center gap-6">
        <a href="/" class="font-semibold">Financial Analysis</a>
        <a href="/models" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-white">Models</a>
        <a href="/analysis" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-white">Analysis</a>
      </div>
    </nav>
    <main class="pt-20 max-w-2xl mx-auto p-6 space-y-4">
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold">Static Nav Page</h1>
      <p>No JavaScript enhancement runs here. If this nav renders consistently while the dynamic one does not, the issue lies in interactive scripts.</p>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
